  ```python Python
  from notte_sdk import NotteClient

  client = NotteClient()

  with client.Session(
      headless=True,
      solve_captchas=True,
      proxies=True,
      viewport_width=1920,
      viewport_height=1080,
      timeout_minutes=10,
      browser_type="chromium"
  ) as session:
      page = session.page
      page.goto("https://example.com")
  ```
